canonical:
  title: 暮春聞鶯
  author: 林椿
  language: lzh
  text: 田家葚熟麥將稠綠樹時聞黃栗留似識洛陽花下客殷勤百囀未能休
  rtl: true
  vertical: true
lzh_formatted:
  title: 暮春聞鶯
  author: 林椿
  language: lzh
  text: 田家葚熟麥將稠。綠樹時聞黃栗留。似識洛陽花下客。殷勤百囀未能休。
korean:
  title: 저문 봄 꾀꼬리 소리를 들으며
  author: 임춘
  language: kor
  text: |-
    전가에 오디 익으니 보리가 장차 한물일세
    푸른 나무 때때로 꾀꼬리 머무나니
    낙양의 꽃 아래 손님 아는 양하여
    은근히 울고울어 쉬지를 않네
  url: https://db.itkc.or.kr/dir/item?itemId=BT#dir/node?dataId=ITKC_BT_1365A_0220_020_0880&viewSync=OT
english:
  title: Hearing the Oriole in Late Spring
  author: Lim Chun
  language: eng
  text: |-
    The mulberries ripen in the fields, and barley grows thick,
    Green trees echo with the yellow oriole's song.
    As if knowing the guest beneath the flowers of Luoyang,
    It trills and chirps with tender persistence, never ceasing.
  footnotes:
    - 'Luoyang: The ancient capital of China, a classical allusion to refined culture and romance in Chinese poetry'
